  "texts": [
    "• Conducting a systematic review of LLM capabilities, training processes, and applications in educational settings [14,15].",
    "• Providing practical case studies to illustrate real-world challenges, opportunities, and solutions in implementing LLMs.By systematically bridging the existing gaps and offering a structured framework, this study highlights the potential of LLMs to transform teaching and learning while addressing key challenges.",
    "Motivation of the studyThis study is motivated by the transformative impact of ChatGPT and LLMs across disciplines, particularly in education, healthcare, finance, coding, and the job market.In education, LLMs like ChatGPT revolutionize learning by virtualizing processes, expanding opportunities, and reshaping pedagogical approaches.",
    "Their potential to automate tasks, enhance personalized learning, and improve accessibility highlights their significance.Other sectors also demonstrate their impact:• Healthcare: Assisting in medical diagnosis, research, and knowledge dissemination [8].Fig. 1 Architecture of LLMs for education Contribution of the studyThe main contributions of this article are as follows:• Comprehensive Background and Theoretical Foundation: The study begins by providing an extensive background on the evolution of educational systems, LLMs, and the concept of intelligent education.",
    "It clarifies the relationship between LLMs and education and explores the notion of \"Smart Education\" as a transformative paradigm, setting the stage for the practical and theoretical insights presented."
  ]
